            "value": [
                "DISNEY MOANA STYLING HEAD – The officially licensed Disney Princess styling head toy set features one of Disney’s most iconic princesses – Moana! The doll has Moana’s beautiful thick hair that is perfect for brushing, styling and practicing new hair styles on.",
                "13 CUTE HAIR ACCESSORIES – The styling head doll for girls comes with 13 cute “wear and share” accessories that your child can use to accessorize Moana or wear for themselves – 1 hair brush, 3 hair spirals, 1 hair barrette, 4 elastic bands and 4 seashell clips.",
